}
```

**batch script to create concatenated angular8app.js:**
`ng build angular8-custom --prod --output-hashing=none && type "dist\angular8-custom\runtime-es2015.js" "dist\angular8-custom\polyfills-es2015.js" "dist\angular8-custom\scripts.js" "dist\angular8-custom\main-es2015.js" > "output\angular8app.js"`

**angular8app.js**: The script file for the angular element app, which is a concat of "runtime.js, main.js and polyfills.js"

**app-custom-element**: The custom element tag, defined in app.module

**app-root**: The app root of the embedded angular8 cli generated application.

**Other scripts**: Scripts for the angular8 cli generated application.

